{
  "stem": "9590.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do not remember any killing or any scandals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Life was placid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Among us in school, it was also a very pleasant atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No animosity, just pure rivalry between students.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No crime whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1938, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I remember, in the house, my parents spoke about the fact that Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They read the book and somehow, they saw that there will be big changes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did not think that it will affect us directly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but they felt uneasy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just like Herman [NON-ENGLISH] said, 'the winds were blowing in our direction.' We as children did not feel it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother was three years younger, a very playful, very handsome little boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when he came in to the house, he was very, very cheerful and smiling and happy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was serious, but I did not pay much attention to the political situation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But in 1939, after I came back from the gimnazjum after the vacation, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the first day, when I was supposed to return back for the other term, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was September in 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did not go to Rowne, anymore because the bombs were bombing our little shtetl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my parents wanted to protect me, and they said, you cannot go now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's see what will happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In no time, the Germans [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went forward.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as I started to be interested in politics, I want to know what's going on and what will happen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I read in the papers that Hitler and Stalin made a pact between themselves, and Poland was divided into two parts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Our part became Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
